{"id":"31cd025de9be7624336078d1ac6b17d635a7bd9802a11be42668bce69a1f7f5a","item_id":"450e2d49eb:0","text":"为外观开发创建转台时，渲染带有环境和地面的对象会很有用，可用于照明和反射。"}
{"id":"6efee9543aac4df51596c7248512e02041c60bf2238ce423bc2cc8d0c56fc71d","item_id":"450e2d49eb:1","text":"此 pattern 旨在与高动态范围图像（HDRI）配合使用，通常是摄影捕获环境的 OpenEXR 文件；该环境也作为光源，并使用一个"}
{"id":"1212e2ab64a08ec5ced8175eb4e0b702d7cfc550ede4593bd2ead1444ee69a02","item_id":"450e2d49eb:2","text":"PxrDomeLight"}
{"id":"b570c1ce0bb3269dbeaefca071cd69aeeb48715e847c2fa1a67c1350352140c3","item_id":"450e2d49eb:3","text":"。然后将此 pattern 连接到你的地面几何体材质。"}
{"id":"4cfe631df1473663aa2459abc49e67d3e5f6c7a0bfba094fcdb9d61edad9d3aa","item_id":"450e2d49eb:4","text":"Offset 和 Rotation 这类放置控制用于让它与你的 PxrDomeLight 最终放置位置相匹配。"}
{"id":"5ecaeef99a9f6c78ef07a7b53cfc36bc420b61182890bb81fcea5c376795132c","item_id":"450e2d49eb:5","text":"此 pattern 适用于外观开发工作流：将你的资产放在场景原点/中心，以保持正确投射。"}
{"id":"971b974235a86ca628dcc713d6e2e8d975206cc84c858720ce046c2dab72855a","item_id":"450e2d49eb:7","text":"Filename"}
{"id":"ac35b664a794b65b731acdebe0a2ec393f81c3eb4505319f4a588971b6a244b7","item_id":"450e2d49eb:8","text":"在此提供用作地面的 HDRI 纹理。请注意，离原点越远，细节可能会逐渐丢失。"}
{"id":"1a9198bb10ef11aac43b5ce01b6f5a46e43f87fa40256f8332828a8c1777a482","item_id":"450e2d49eb:9","text":"Environment Radius"}
{"id":"7c30b11994c24c61233afff009f0850c03e3e3e2e3faded9bb6eb89c58ec6387","item_id":"450e2d49eb:10","text":"更改所提供投射的距离；不正确的值会导致可见拉伸。"}
{"id":"57e52e87202ad294a88d698027888fb5641feec9caeb993e2d8da5326298109f","item_id":"450e2d49eb:11","text":"Offset X"}
{"id":"00886d86e9d19b17d5a69b5df8aefeb470724a42e38b13a1b0ddace137c204b3","item_id":"450e2d49eb:12","text":"沿 X 方向移动结果。负值会向相反方向移动。"}
{"id":"e25258226964d7bef77a42b4db80357aa2e3e2674e91517ceb0fa0c22f92bc19","item_id":"450e2d49eb:13","text":"Offset Z"}
{"id":"163b3948e285181d606797f6c54ab5cabf8c6e21b18e2e9d0b3f791a8d33fd5f","item_id":"450e2d49eb:14","text":"沿 Y 方向移动结果。负值会向相反方向移动。"}
{"id":"57b5e2fc1bba18bb4f54084af57ffe86b3bb3d925c281043e84a05eb4b19317c","item_id":"450e2d49eb:15","text":"Rotation"}
{"id":"c39ac82015637b23266f64397d7e893565173254d728643d8855571ee08f133d","item_id":"450e2d49eb:16","text":"以度为单位，围绕 Y 轴旋转结果。"}
{"id":"447b88a7a549d041e8465a589d2d193a973e72b99863fe47cdbc6af1a89aa229","item_id":"450e2d49eb:17","text":"Filter Width"}
{"id":"911d14e5f760cdbe8526bb39a230346f06c74851f8a09e8c95f1698a3ecee19a","item_id":"450e2d49eb:18","text":"可用于模糊纹理结果。"}
{"id":"2a5a9456d3b203e2d154720c4279730eaa9070b4cfb8c2a35cb247ea0e4557ff","item_id":"450e2d49eb:20","text":"ResultRGB"}
{"id":"20c8c3c70a442b8b037ab0b4a66223e5a0ca9d73d373b6fd7dc4257d21890ba7","item_id":"450e2d49eb:21","text":"通常连接到材质的 Diffuse color 输入。"}
{"id":"ffbed86cffcac1567839d8d5cb3e8d1694123a37b5e171d50fc0a1820b41a135","item_id":"450e2d49eb:22","text":"Result Presence"}
{"id":"557658269b2ba96ae984e06670c57ee5b234f2b1149a18b8393ed7b3b60486ff","item_id":"450e2d49eb:23","text":"连接到材质的 Presence 参数。"}
{"id":"b19842f9d4ea8bd7b39f8738d49e7ec34ce09c1de2214f1efe1d28cd54ec6208","item_id":"450e2d49eb:24","text":"ResultNG"}
{"id":"63b6b20f3121733aed855322daf316bc6e1c2ba6a6c1021312d34ad60b888244","item_id":"450e2d49eb:25","text":"这会连接到一个"}
{"id":"fbf44a5013ff1e3bb2067a0bda5e361e18e4411bfa5be60ee9012dd95f737fb7","item_id":"450e2d49eb:26","text":"PxrBumpMixer"}
{"id":"928a8eb83eda8930a0a02048a0b3f8cfc297e28cbd887e9149d411069f7befc7","item_id":"450e2d49eb:27","text":"（必需），然后再连接到材质的 Normal/Bump 参数，通常是 global bump（全局 bump，如果存在）。"}
{"id": "e8756d05615a8b9aac2d138a9ae82553f3231ff237868a66679a30001b4f326b", "item_id": "450e2d49eb:6", "text": "Input Parameters（输入参数）"}
{"id": "b2439bcb8dee14b685f137f294b0e0cb62f5aadf45143ce01d79777d435a93b4", "item_id": "450e2d49eb:19", "text": "Output"}
